{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"362","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"防堵洋垃圾 廢紙廢塑料輸入新制上路","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>台灣廢紙、廢塑料進口量大增，引發洋垃圾大舉侵台質疑，為防堵洋垃圾，環保署今天公告修正廢塑膠及廢紙輸入規定，包含進口者只限合法工廠、廢塑膠限單一材質、單一型態等。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>環保署表示，根據廢塑膠及廢紙進口情形，今年3月發現有進口量上升情形，就啟動廢塑膠及廢紙進口業者稽查及實地查訪，統計107年1至7月廢塑膠進口量較去年同期增加約15萬噸，廢紙則較去年同期增加約19萬噸。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>行政院環境保護署今天修正發布「屬產業用料需求之事業廢棄物」，加嚴進口廢塑膠及廢紙規定，修正重點為增加要求熱塑型廢塑膠來源，僅限單一材質或單一型態的塑膠製程下腳料或不良品，或其他非塑膠製程來源的廢塑膠，須為單一材質及單一型態，且均不得附著土壤，並限制進口者以合法工廠為限。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>另外，廢紙則僅限回收且經妥善分類的牛皮紙、瓦楞紙或脫墨紙，並限制進口者身分為紙或紙製品製造業者，讓合法且有實際需求的製造業進口使用再生物料。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>環保署表示，業者若未遵守相關規定，一經查獲，將予以嚴懲，除依法要求全數退運原輸出國外，也將依廢棄物清理法告發，處新台幣6萬元以上、1000萬元以下之罰鍰。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>資料來源：https://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/201810010193.aspx</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-10-18","clk_count":"255"}},"__N_SSG":true}